# Media Directory

This directory stores user-uploaded files (images, documents, etc.).

## Purpose

- Contains user uploads
- Served by Nginx in production
- Managed by Django's FileField/ImageField

## Security

- Files are served through Nginx with proper headers
- Maximum upload size controlled by Django and Nginx settings
- Content type validation performed by Django

**Note:** This directory is excluded from Git (except this .gitkeep file) as it contains user-generated content.
